%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Starbucks%20is%20copying%20the%20fast-food%20value%20playbook%20with%20its%20new%20%245%20and%20%246%20breakfast%20combos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20from%20Starbucks'%20website%20showing%20its%20two%20new%20combo%20deals%20available%20under%20its%20Pairings%20Menu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6669807ae07904901818022c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221096%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStarbucks%20has%20launched%20two%20breakfast%20combo%20deals%2C%20pairing%20a%20coffee%20or%20tea%20with%20a%20croissant%20or%20breakfast%20sandwich.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOnly%20a%20limited%20range%20of%20drinks%20appear%20to%20be%20included%2C%20but%20you%20can%20pay%20extra%20to%20customize%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBundling%20has%20long%20been%20standard%20practice%20in%20fast-food%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20surprise%20move%20for%20Starbucks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20unusual%20move%20for%20the%20coffee%20giant%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-coffee-howard-schultz-steve-jobs-bill-gates-acquired-podcast-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarbucks%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20getting%20into%20bundling%20by%20offering%20new%20%245%20and%20%246%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20launched%20the%20two%20combo%20deals%20on%20Tuesday%20under%20what%20it%20calls%20its%20%26quot%3Bpairings%20menu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20can%20get%20a%2012-ounce%20iced%20or%20hot%20coffee%20or%20tea%20paired%20with%20a%20butter%20croissant%20from%20%245%2C%20or%20with%20a%20breakfast%20sandwich%20from%20%246.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2222f6a57d-824d-476c-8643-999abbec2d71%5C%22%3EStarbucks'%20US%20sales%20have%20been%20slumping%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBundling%20has%20long%20been%20standard%20practice%20in%20the%20fast-food%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20think%20of%20all%20the%20burger%20chains%20that%20let%20you%20make%20your%20order%20a%20meal%20by%20adding%20fries%20and%20a%20drink%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20extra%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20a%20surprise%20move%20for%20Starbucks.%20In%20its%20marketing%2C%20the%20coffee%20chain%20has%20tended%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20quality%20and%20range%20of%20its%20products%20rather%20than%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Henkes%2C%20senior%20principal%20at%20foodservice%20research%20company%20Technomic%2C%20told%20CNN%20that%20Starbucks%20had%20%26quot%3Bin%20many%20ways%20been%20a%20symbol%20of%20affordable%20indulgence%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20company%20seemingly%20now%20felt%20that%20%26quot%3Btheir%20affordability%20has%20softened%20to%20the%20degree%20that%20they%20need%20to%20use%20deals%20to%20drive%20traffic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20posted%20poor%20earnings%20earlier%20this%20year.%20In%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-starbucks-earnings-how-cautious-us-consumers-spending-sales-decline-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarbucks'%20comparable%20US%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%20declined%203%25%20year-over-year%2C%20with%20a%207%25%20drop%20in%20the%20number%20of%20comparable%20transactions.%20CEO%20Laxman%20Narasimhan%20called%20the%20results%20%26quot%3Bdisappointing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20feel%20the%20impact%20of%20a%20more%20cautious%20consumer%2C%26quot%3B%20Narasimhan%20told%20investors%20at%20the%20company's%20latest%20earnings%20call%2C%20adding%20that%20some%20customers%20had%20been%20saving%20money%20by%20eating%20more%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Starbucks.%20Other%20restaurant%20executives%20have%20echoed%20Narasimhan's%20comments%2C%20saying%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-prices-increases-consumers-weary-mcdonalds-wendys-starbucks-kfc-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediners%20are%20cutting%20back%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20fast-food%20chains%20have%20introduced%20new%20offers%20and%20vowed%20to%20stop%20hiking%20prices%20to%20win%20back%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295ae38d9-b3b8-44a6-9d1c-6e7a45f15b0d%5C%22%3EIt's%20easy%20for%20the%20price%20of%20Starbucks'%20combo%20deals%20to%20rack%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20has%20six%20items%20in%20its%20breakfast%20sandwich%20range.%20Choosing%20the%20double-smoked%20bacon%2C%20cheddar%2C%20and%20egg%20sandwich%20and%20the%20Impossible%20breakfast%20sandwich%20puts%20the%20bundle's%20price%20up%20by%20%241%20to%20%247.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks'%20prices%20vary%20considerably%20by%20location.%20At%20a%20Starbucks%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20ordering%20a%20butter%20croissant%20costs%20%244.45%2C%20while%20two%20of%20the%20breakfast%20sandwiches%20cost%20%245.45%2C%20and%20four%20cost%20%246.45.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20in%20the%20mood%20for%20a%20croissant%20or%20sandwich%20and%20a%20drink%2C%20the%20combo%20can%20save%20you%20considerable%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20want%20to%20customize%20your%20drink%20then%20the%20prices%20start%20to%20rack%20up.%20When%20Business%20Insider%20added%20sauce%20and%20cold%20foam%20to%20a%20tall%20Starbucks%20Iced%20Coffee%20Blend%2C%20the%20price%20of%20the%20croissant%20and%20coffee%20deal%20went%20up%20from%20%245%20to%20%247.45%20at%20the%20Manhattan%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20upgrade%20the%20size%20of%20your%20drink%20for%20an%20extra%20charge%2C%20though%20it%20appears%20you%20get%20less%20of%20a%20discount%20overall.%20Upgrading%20a%20tall%20Iced%20Coffee%20Blend%20with%20no%20modifications%20to%20the%2024-ounce%20venti%20version%20brings%20the%20croissant%20deal%20to%20%246%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20%241%2C%20despite%20a%20venti%20Iced%20Coffee%20Blend%20only%20costing%20%240.50%20more%20than%20a%20tall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20drinks%20included%20in%20the%20deal%20include%20some%20hot%20coffees%2C%20like%20Starbucks'%20Decaf%20Pike%20Place%20Roast%20and%20Veranda%20Blend%20Clover%20Vertica%2C%20hot%20teas%2C%20like%20its%20Royal%20English%20Breakfast%20tea%2C%20and%20iced%20teas%2C%20like%20its%20iced%20black%20tea.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20drinks%20didn't%20appear%20to%20be%20eligible%20when%20ordering%20for%20collection%20via%20Starbucks'%20website%2C%20including%20cappuccinos%2C%20Americanos%2C%20cold%20brew%2C%20tea%20lattes%2C%20and%20some%20of%20its%20iced%20green%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20notes%20that%20the%20two%20combos%20are%20only%20limited-time%20offers%2C%20although%20it%20doesn't%20say%20how%20long%20the%20promotions%20will%20last.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F06%2F11%2Ffood%2Fstarbucks-value-breakfast-menu%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20offer%20is%20available%20all%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIs%20fast%20food%20too%20expensive%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%20at%20gdean%40insider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-bundling-breakfast-combo-deals-sandwich-croissant-tea-coffee-meal-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718191569000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6669806de079049018180227%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-bundling-breakfast-combo-deals-sandwich-croissant-tea-coffee-meal-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bundling%20has%20long%20been%20a%20standard%20practice%20in%20the%20fast-food%20industry%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20surprise%20move%20for%20Starbucks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-bundling-breakfast-combo-deals-s