inese%20goods%2C%20including%20a%20100%25%20tax%20on%20Chinese%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese-branded%20EVs%20have%20almost%20no%20presence%20in%20the%20US%2C%20thanks%20to%20existing%20trade%20barriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Europe%2C%20they%20have%20been%20making%20steady%20inroads%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-ev-companies-shut-out-of-us-target-mexico-brazil-2024-%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20rival%20BYD%20building%20a%20factory%20in%20Hungary%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20startups%20Nio%20and%20Xpeng%20releasing%20models%20in%20several%20European%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20brands%20rose%20from%20under%201%25%20of%20Europe's%20EV%20market%20in%202019%20to%208%25%20in%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europarl.europa.eu%2FRegData%2Fetudes%2FATAG%2F2023%2F754553%2FEPRS_ATA(2023)754553_EN.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20European%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20hit%2015%25%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20crackdown%2C%20Philip%20Nothard%2C%20insight%20and%20strategy%20director%20at%20automotive%20services%20company%20Cox%20Automotive%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20measures%20will%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20keep%20Chinese%20EV%20companies%20at%20bay%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20with%20tariffs%2C%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20slow%20the%20growth%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Nothard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20companies%20like%20BYD%2C%20they%20have%20a%20highly%20efficient%20manufacturing%20supply%20chain.%20That%20makes%20them%20extremely%20agile%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20changing%20products%20for%20different%20marketplaces%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20suggesting%20that%20Chinese%20companies%20could%20adjust%20their%20growth%20plans%20to%20keep%20prices%20low%20even%20with%20new%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trade%20barriers%2