sinsider.com%2Fnews-today-november-18-work-life-balance-job-careers-remote-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebalance%20work%20with%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20challenging%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoing-back-to-work-after-baby-maternity-leave-judgment-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoms%20often%20let%20themselves%20feel%20guilty%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20If%20we%20spend%20too%20much%20time%20at%20home%2C%20we%20have%20work%20guilt%2C%20and%20if%20we%20spend%20too%20much%20time%20at%20work%2C%20we%20have%20mom%20guilt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20job%20is%20very%20rewarding%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20stressful%20and%20physically%20and%20mentally%20demanding.%20I%20have%20very%20ill%20patients%20and%20sometimes%20have%20to%20make%20high-level%20decisions.%20Cases%20can%20take%2030%20minutes%20or%20eight%20hours%20to%20manage%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20often%20sure%20when%20I'll%20be%20done%20for%20the%20day.%20It%20could%20be%204%3A30%20p.m.%20or%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20get%20home%20for%20around%206%20p.m.%2C%20but%20it's%20never%20predictable.%20If%20I%20know%20there's%20no%20way%20I'll%20be%20home%20for%20dinner%2C%20I'll%20text%20Ray%20to%20let%20him%20know%20so%20he%20can%20plan%20to%20spend%20the%20evening%20with%20the%20kids%20as%20he%20desires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I'm%20on%20call%20for%20my%20job%2C%20I'm%20not%20required%20to%20be%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20I%20have%20to%20be%20prepared%20to%20respond%20and%20go%20there%20if%20need%20be.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20Ray%20would%20usually%20be%20around%20to%20look%20after%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20receive%20calls%20at%20home%20and%20have%20to%20open%20up%20scans%20on%20my%20computer%20to%20make%20important%20decisions%20about%20a%20case.%20I%20sometimes%20have%20to%20ask%20my%20kids%20to%20give%20me%20five%20minutes%20while%20I%20put%20them%20to%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20they're%20understanding.%20They%20know%20mommy%20