n%20tips.%20The%20spokesperson%20added%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-us-economy-would-look-like-with-trump-biden-presidency-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20aggressively%20stepped%20up%20the%20IRS%20going%20after%20tip%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20IRS%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Firs-introduces-new-service-industry-tip-reporting-program%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprogram%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20to%20encourage%20voluntary%20compliance%20with%20reporting%20rules%2C%20none%20of%20the%20tax%20experts%20who%20spoke%20with%20BI%20could%20identify%20a%20new%20Biden%20administration%20policy%20targeting%20tipped%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20did%20not%20provide%20any%20details%20about%20the%20proposal%2C%20an%20economist%20and%20two%20tax%20law%20experts%20told%20BI%20it%20would%20insert%20more%20complexity%20in%20the%20tax%20code%20without%20offering%20any%20substantial%20benefits%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrivers-and-servers-share-how-they-earn-extra-money%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etipped%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224bdfe51f-ff65-44be-8c7d-d768bfddb4ec%5C%22%3EThe%20policy%20would%20create%20a%20massive%20tax%20loophole%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20think%20you%20get%20asked%20for%20tips%20a%20lot%20now%2C%20just%20wait%20until%20tips%20aren't%20taxed%2C%26quot%3B%20Martha%20Gimbel%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Yale%20University's%20Budget%20Lab%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20She%20added%20that%20a%20new%20system%20would%20only%20create%20%26quot%3Ban%20incentive%20for%20employers%20to%20try%20to%20get%20more%20of%20their%20workers'%20compensation%20in%20the%20form%20of%20tips.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20passed%2C%20Gimbel%20noted%2