%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHenrik%20Fisker's%20second%20automotive%20startup%20is%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20pitched%20as%20a%20Tesla%20rival%2C%20but%20workers%20say%20mismanagement%20and%20cutting%20corners%20led%20to%20compounding%20problems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%2027%20former%20and%20current%20Fisker%20staff%20that%20charted%20the%20startup's%20downfall.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-ocean-range-360-mile-tesla-model-y-extreme-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFisker's%3C%2Fa%3E%20staff%20was%20in%20chaos%20as%20they%20prepared%20to%20deliver%20the%20company's%20first%20batch%20of%20electric%20cars%20to%20US%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20been%20four%20years%20since%20famed%20automotive%20designer%20Henrik%20Fisker%20unveiled%20his%20Tesla%20rival%2C%20an%20SUV%20called%20the%20Ocean%2C%20and%20the%20vehicle%20still%20wasn't%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20big%20June%202023%20event%2C%20Fisker%20staff%20raced%20to%20fix%20faulty%20parts%20on%20at%20least%20four%20of%20the%2022%20EVs%20that%20were%20set%20to%20be%20delivered%20%E2%80%94%20even%20stripping%20parts%20off%20the%20CEO%20and%20CFO's%20personal%20cars%20to%20repair%20the%20vehicles%2C%20including%20door%20handles%20and%20seat%20sensors%2C%20according%20to%2011%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20Fisker%20board%20member%20Wendy%20Gruel's%20Ocean%20SUV%2C%20one%20of%20the%20cars%20that%20had%20been%20delivered%20at%20the%20event%2C%20shut%20off%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20a%20public%20road%20while%20going%20full%20speed%2C%20five%20sources%20said.%20Later%2C%20the%20same%20thing%20happened%20to%20Geeta%20Gupta-Fisker%2C%20Henrik's%20wife%20and%20the%20company's%20CFO%20and%20COO%2C%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20denied%20that%20workers%20used%20parts%20from%20pre-production%20vehicles%20for%20customer%20cars%20and%20said%20Gruel's%20car%20didn't%20stop%20on%20a%20public%20road.%20The%20company%20said%20Gupta-Fisker's%20vehicle%20had%20malfunctioned%2C%20but%20the%20issue%20was%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2024%2F02%2F09%2Ffisker-ocean-braking-power-loss-problems-investigation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETechCrunch%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20incident%20with%20Gruel's%20car%2C%20the%20publication%20said%20the%20company%20had%20confirmed%20the%20incident%20and%20said%20the%20issue%20was%20fixed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20was%20unrelated%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-fixing-some-evs-with-parts-from-inventory-vehicles-sources-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFisker's%20part%20swapping%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20was%20clear%3A%20the%20electric%20cars%20had%20barely%20hit%20the%20road%20and%20already%20the%20problems%20were%20piling%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHenrik%20Fisker's%20EV%20startup%20seemed%20to%20be%20an%20easy%20sell%20at%20first.%20The%2060-year-old%20automotive%20veteran%20boasts%20a%20long%20history%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20known%20for%20being%20the%20designer%20behind%20the%20Aston%20Martin%20V8%2C%20the%20BMW%20Z8%20roadster%20that%20famously%20appeared%20in%20a%201999%20James%20Bond%20film%2C%20and%20helping%20design%20Tesla's%20Model%20S.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20it%20was%20Henrik's%20second%20automotive%20startup%20after%20his%20first%20company%20went%20out%20of%20business%20in%202013%2C%20some%20workers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20dismiss%20worries%20early%20on%20that%20his%20second%20company%20could%20meet%20the%20same%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20part%2C%20Henrik%20said%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fcar-designer-henrik-fisker-lost-his-first-race-with-elon-musk-he-wants-to-go-again-11596811140%3Fmod%3Darticle_inline%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanned%20to%20do%20things%20differently%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20time.%20He%20would%20follow%20Apple's%20model%20by%20outsourcing%20production%20through%20Magna%20International%20and%20he%20also%20aimed%20to%20target%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20market%20with%20a%20more%20affordable%20EV%20option%20that%20could%20compete%20with%20Tesla's%20best-selling%20Model%20Y.%20Fisker%20Inc%20emerged%20in%202016%20and%20went%20public%20in%202020%20via%20a%20SPAC%20backed%20by%20Apollo%20Global%20Management.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20the%20company's%20market%20value%20soared%20as%20high%20as%20%248%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Fisker%20was%20one%20of%20several%20EV%20startups%20to%20burst%20onto%20the%20scene%20%E2%80%94%20Rivian%2C%20Lucid%2C%20and%20Lordstown%20all%20wanted%20the%20chance%20to%20compete%20with%20Tesla.%20Since%20then%2C%20production%20and%20market%20headwinds%20have%20pushed%20some%20EV%20startups%20to%20shutter%20and%20major%20players%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-cuts-production-of-f150-lightning-cybertruck-rival-ev-demand-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFord%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20GM%20to%20scale%20back%20their%20electric-vehicle%20operations.%20Even%20Tesla%20has%20struggled%2C%20seeing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-rough-year-sales-slump-layoffs-china-ev-competition-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevenue%20decline%20and%20layoffs.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20hopeful%20at%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20VP%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20both%20Fisker%20startups%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BInitially%2C%20at%20least%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20he'd%20learned%20from%20his%20mistakes.%20It%20became%20obvious%20later%20on%20that%20they%20hadn't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20said%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bunfair%26quot%3B%20to%20compare%20the%20two%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20company%20is%20fighting%20for%20its%20life%2C%20pulling%20out%20all%20the%20stops%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20avoid%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20over%20two%20dozen%20current%20and%20former%20Fisker%20employees%20who%20worked%20at%20the%20startup%20during%20various%20periods%20from%20its%20launch%20in%202016%20to%20the%20present.%20The%20workers%2C%20whose%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20BI%2C%20requested%20anonymity%20as%20they%20were%20not%20authorized%20to%20comment%20on%20Fisker's%20behalf%20and%20feared%20professional%20reprisal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8954edd-4b73-4f38-85d2-814ed075f355%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20husband%20and%20wife%20duo%20who%20workers%20say%20mismanaged%20their%20way%20into%20a%20mess%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20Fisker's%20woes%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20the%20husband-wife%20duo%20that%20launched%20the%20brand%2C%20multiple%20former%20and%20current%20workers%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20described%20a%20disorganized%20environment%20in%20which%20unqualified%20people%20were%20brought%20in%20to%20lead%20major%20programs%20and%20basic%20automotive%20standards%20were%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Henrik%20often%20served%20as%20a%20figurehead%2C%20Gupta-Fisker%20was%20heavily%20involved%20in%20everyday%20decisions%2C%20including%20on%20the%20engineering%20side%2C%2011%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eworkers%20said.%20Prior%20to%20taking%20on%20the%20role%20of%20CFO%20and%20COO%20at%20Fisker%2C%20Gupta-Fisker%20had%20served%20as%20an%20investment%20manager%20for%20the%20Fisker%20family%20office%20and%20as%20an%20advisor%20at%20a%20nonprofit.%20She%20had%20no%20prior%20experience%20in%20the%20automotive%20industry.%20But%20at%20Fisker%2C%20the%20workers%20said%20she%20managed%20deals%20with%20Magna%20and%20outside%20parts%20suppliers%2C%20frequently%20popped%20into%20engineering%20meetings%2C%20and%20weighed%20in%20on%20everything%20from%20parts%20purchases%20to%20software%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Magna%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Fisker.%20A%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20denied%20comments%20that%20Henrik%20took%20on%20a%20more%20passive%20role%20and%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20involved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22henrik%20fisker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5805227bc5240220008b4dea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22798%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHenrik%20Fisker%20shows%20off%20the%20Fisker%20Karma.%20The%20car%20he%20produced%20under%20his%20first%20automotive%20venture%2C%20which%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20a%20decade%20ago.%3Cp%3EReuters%2FPhil%20McCarten%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E49-year-old%20Gupta-Fisker%20quickly%20became%20known%20in%20the%20company%20for%20her%20shrewd%20cost-cutting%20abilities.%20But%2C%20her%20strategy%20meant%20that%20at%20times%20Fisker%20ended%20up%20using%20components%20that%20didn't%20match%20the%20correct%20specifications%20for%20the%20Ocean%2C%20five%20former%20and%20current%20workers%20said.%20Gupta-Fisker%20made%20several%20decisions%20to%20use%20cheaper%20parts%20against%20Fisker%20executive%20and%20Magana%20executives'%20advice%2C%20two%20workers%20said.%20The%20mismatches%20led%20to%20issues%20with%20over-the-air%20updates%2C%20the%20five%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20Magna%20oversaw%20the%20majority%20of%20parts%20sourcing%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20amount%20of%20the%20parts%20came%20from%20Magna%20and%20its%20suppliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20conversations%20with%20BI%2C%20staff%20blamed%20many%20of%20the%20Ocean's%20faults%20on%20the%20cost-cutting%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20workers%20said%20that%20in%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20vehicle's%20launch%2C%20they%20filed%20internal%20reports%20recommending%20that%20the%20product%20undergo%20further%20testing%20and%20development%20before%20its%20release.%20They%20said%20they%20were%20told%20the%20company%20planned%20to%20proceed%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20focus%20was%20on%20getting%20the%20car%20to%20market%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20worker%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20overarching%20belief%20was%20we%20could%20fix%20things%20with%20updates%20later%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20said%20Magna%20was%20responsible%20for%20testing%20and%20releasing%20the%20Ocean%20and%20it%20had%20been%20fully%20certified%20by%20regulators%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe.%20The%20company%20has%20been%20sending%20out%20over-the-air%20updates%20since%202023%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20release%2C%20Fisker%20engineers%20were%20aware%20of%20multiple%20issues%20with%20the%20vehicle%2C%20according%20to%20five%20current%20and%20former%20workers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20internal%20documents%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20Engineers%20had%20identified%20issues%20with%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20car's%20door%20handles%2C%20key%20fobs%2C%20and%20seat%20sensors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20National%20Highway%20Traffic%20Safety%20Administration%20(NHTSA)%20has%20launched%20four%20investigations%20into%20Fisker's%20SUV%2C%20including%20issues%20with%20inadvertent%20braking%20and%20flaws%20in%20the%20vehicle's%20door%20latch%20system.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20is%20cooperating%20with%20NHTSA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisker%20has%20also%20faced%20dozens%20of%20lemon%20law%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e98472b-4e09-47d7-bcfa-881e8d846bb4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECutting%20corners%20led%20to%20compounding%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20haste%20to%20bring%20the%20car%20to%20market%2C%20Fisker%20failed%20to%20set%20up%20an%20effective%20system%20for%20processing%20repair%20orders%20and%20warranty%20claims%2C%20seven%20current%20and%20former%20workers%20said.%20Technicians%20were%20tasked%20with%20filling%20out%20the%20work%20orders%20and%20many%20of%20them%20said%20they%20hadn't%20been%20trained%20on%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20lieu%20of%20a%20working%20warranty%20system%2C%20some%20workers%20began%20processing%20the%20repairs%20without%20the%20proper%20California%20Bureau%20of%20Automotive%20Repair%20codes%20and%20EPA%20license%20numbers%2C%20using%20%26quot%3B123456%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20placeholder%20on%20a%20number%20of%20repairs%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20document%20viewed%20by%20BI.%20In%20March%2C%20a%20VP%20at%20Fisker%20warned%20the%20issue%20made%20the%20company%20non-compliant%20with%20NHTSA%20protocols%20and%20unable%20to%20properly%20track%20and%20report%20safety%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20issue%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20internal%20error%20with%20only%20draft%20work%20orders%20early%20in%20the%20service%20process%20that%20was%20immediately%20corrected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Fisker%20Ocean%20electric%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6453d9aadcb78700180ce3c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222180%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fisker%20Ocean%20hit%20US%20roads%20in%20June%202023.%3Cp%3EFisker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20a%20proper%20system%20to%20process%20warranties%20or%20repair%20orders%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20repairs%20went%20unaccounted%20for%2C%20seven%20current%20and%20former%20workers%20said.%20That%20meant%20there%20wasn't%20an%20adequate%20way%20for%20Fisker%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20which%20parts%20were%20being%20used%20for%20repairs%20for%20its%20own%20financial%20records.%20It%20also%20meant%20many%20customers%20did%20not%20get%20a%20record%20of%20their%20repairs%2C%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Fisker%20also%20struggled%20to%20find%20the%20necessary%20parts%20for%20all%20of%20the%20fixes.%20The%20company%20hadn't%20set%20up%20much%20inventory%20for%20aftersales%20parts%2C%20so%20some%20of%20the%20parts%20used%20for%20customer%20fixes%20either%20came%20directly%20off%20the%20factory%20line%2C%20meaning%20they%20were%20meant%20for%20production%20vehicles%2C%20or%20the%20parts%20were%20stripped%20off%20pre-production%20and%20production%20vehicles%2C%2011%20workers%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20issue%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20instance%2C%20Fisker%20stripped%20parts%20off%20an%20engineering%20test%20vehicle%20that%20had%20been%20shipped%20from%20Magna's%20facility%20in%20Graz%2C%20Austria%20under%20an%20import%20bond%2C%20according%20to%20three%20former%20workers%20and%20emails%20viewed%20by%20BI.%20The%20vehicle%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20destroyed%20in%20its%20entirety%20shortly%20after%20it%20was%20delivered%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20import.%20The%20vehicle's%20parts%20were%20not%20intended%20to%20be%20used%20for%20customers'%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20denied%20any%20test%20vehicles%20had%20been%20used%20for%20parts%20and%20said%20all%20vehicles%20that%20had%20been%20imported%20for%20testing%20were%20destroyed%20under%20NHTSA's%20supervision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20also%20denied%20that%20Fisker%20had%20a%20shortage%20of%20after-sales%20parts%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Service%20department%20made%20its%20own%20forecast%20for%20parts%2C%20based%20on%20their%20sector%20knowledge.%20The%20Purchasing%20department%20supported%20those%20requests.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisker%20staff%20also%20looked%20for%20clever%20ways%20to%20address%20the%20parts%20shortage.%20In%20some%20instances%2C%20workers%20who%20visited%20Graz%20were%20told%20by%20managers%20to%20bring%20parts%20back%20in%20their%20suitcases%20to%20avoid%20paying%20import%20fees%2C%20seven%20workers%20said.%20One%20worker%20recalled%20having%20to%20leave%20personal%20belongings%20behind%20to%20fit%20air%20vents%20and%20key%20fobs%20into%20their%20luggage%3B%20another%20said%20they%20packed%20a%20larger%20bag%20to%20fit%20trim%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisker%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e953bce8-39b3-440c-9715-39f271372785%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20sales%20scramble%20amid%20negative%20reviews%20and%20vanishing%20demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFisker%20was%20initially%20successful%20in%20generating%20interest%20in%20the%20Ocean%2C%20with%20over%2065%2C000%20reservations%20initially%20placed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20year%20since%20the%20Ocean's%20release%2C%20the%20company%20has%20delivered%20around%207%2C000%20vehicles%2C%20a%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20said.%20Negative%20reviews%20%E2%80%94%20including%20YouTuber%20MKBHD%20calling%20it%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmkbhd-fisker-ocean-review-marques-brownlee-video-tiktok-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bworst%20care%20I've%20ever%20reviewed%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20brand%2C%20driving%20thousands%20of%20would-be%20customers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-ocean-reservation-cancellations-electric-car-leaked-data-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecancel%20their%20reservations.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20Fisker%20moved%20to%20bring%20in%20hiring%20recruiters%20to%20help%20sell%20the%20vehicle%2C%20as%20well%20as%20orchestrate%20the%20delivery%20of%20the%20car%20after%20the%20sale%20had%20been%20processed%2C%20six%20former%20workers%20said.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20recruiters%2C%20who%20had%20initially%20been%20brought%20onto%20the%20human%20resources%20team%2C%20had%20zero%20experience%20in%20automotive%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20recruiting%20staff%20did%20join%20the%20sales%20efforts%2C%20though%20the%20company%20said%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20stay%20because%20they%20were%20successful%20in%20the%20new%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221694%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marques%20Brownlee%20reviewed%20the%20Fisker%20Ocean%20for%20a%20second%20time.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660ec0531caec1275a6cd424%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarques%20Brownlee%20reviewed%20the%20Fisker%20Ocean%20and%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bthe%20worst%20car%20I've%20ever%20reviewed.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EYouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESelling%20the%20car%20wasn't%20easy%20either.%20The%20recruiters%20found%20themselves%20directly%20competing%20with%20the%20company's%20established%20sales%20team%20and%20there%20weren't%20enough%20leads%20to%20go%20around.%20Four%20former%20workers%20said%20Fisker's%20reservation%20numbers%20included%20many%20duplicate%20names%20in%20its%20count%20and%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20track%20which%20customers%20had%20connected%20with%20a%20sales%20worker.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20some%20people%20on%20the%20reservation%20list%20would%20find%20themselves%20getting%20multiple%20calls%20per%20day%20from%20different%20Fisker%20representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20sales%20workers%20were%20instructed%20to%20target%20customers%20who%20had%20canceled%20their%20orders%20and%20pepper%20them%20with%20calls%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20get%20them%20to%20reverse%20their%20decision%2C%20three%20former%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisker%20also%20began%20hosting%20pop-up%20events%20to%20boost%20sales%2C%20including%20events%20in%20partnership%20with%20fan%20blog%20Fiskerati%2C%20two%20former%20employees%20told%20BI.%20The%20events%20varied%20from%20meetups%20at%20Panera%20parking%20lots%20to%20larger-scale%20test%20drive%20events.%20In%20at%20least%20one%20instance%2C%20the%20event%20was%20shut%20down%20after%20Fisker%20failed%20to%20get%20permission%20from%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20location%2C%20the%20two%20sources%20said.%20Queues%20of%20Fisker%20owners%20that%20needed%20repairs%20also%20showed%20up%20at%20the%20events%2C%20three%20former%20workers%20said.%20Fisker%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20event%20hosted%20at%20Panera%20was%20not%20a%20company%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20sell%20the%20cars%20when%20you'd%20take%20someone%20on%20a%20test%20drive%20and%20any%20number%20of%20error%20messages%20would%20pop%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20worker%20from%20sales%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20time%20went%20on%20and%20it%20became%20clear%20the%20writing%20was%20on%20the%20wall%2C%20we%20became%20even%20more%20honest%20with%20the%20customers%20on%20the%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisker%20said%20it%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20ADAS%20issues%20but%20it%20was%20fixed%20with%20an%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20some%20customers%20who'd%20canceled%20their%20orders%20and%20never%20paid%20for%20the%20car%20ended%20up%20mistakenly%20receiving%20delivery%20of%20the%20vehicle%20anyway%2C%20four%20former%20workers%20said.%20Former%20Fisker%20Ocean%20owner%20Kurt%20Mechling%20told%20BI%20he%20received%20delivery%20of%20the%20vehicle%20before%20he'd%20signed%20off%20on%20the%20order%20or%20had%20his%20payment%20successfully%20processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2024%2F03%2F27%2Ffisker-misplaced-payments-internal-audit-bankruptcy%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFisker%2520lost%2520track%2520of%2520millions%2520of%2520dollars%2520in%2520customer%2520payments%2520for%2520months%2C-Sean%2520O%2527Kane%26amp%3Btext%3DFisker%2520temporarily%2520lost%2520track%2520of%2Cto%2520complete%252C%2520TechCrunch%2520has%2520learned.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETechCrunch%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Fisker%20temporarily%20%26quot%3Blost%20track%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20customer%20payments%26quot%3B%20for%20multiple%20months.%20Four%20workers%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20issue%20confirmed%20to%20BI%20the%20incident%20involving%20misplaced%20payments%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20carmaker%20conducted%20an%20internal%20audit%20in%20December%20over%20the%20issue%2C%20workers%20began%20scrambling%20to%20find%20the%20missing%20payments%20and%20bring%20some%20of%20the%20vehicles%20that%20had%20been%20mistakenly%20delivered%20back%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20workers%20said.%20Some%20workers%20were%20encouraged%20by%20upper%20management%20to%20threaten%20the%20customers%20by%20saying%20they'd%20put%20them%20on%20a%20repossession%20list%20which%20could%20impact%20their%20credit%20score%2C%20the%20former%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20had%20an%20%26quot%3Borganized%20process%26quot%3B%20to%20address%20issues%20with%20vehicles%20that%20had%20not%20been%20paid%20for%20that%20was%20in%20line%20with%20industry%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d075735-437a-44c8-8b3a-477539207853%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFacing%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20repeat%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Fisker%20has%20dropped%20prices%20by%20as%20much%20as%20%2424%2C000%20for%20some%20versions%20of%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20warned%20in%20March%20that%20it%20might%20go%20out%20of%20business%20within%20the%20year.%20The%20stock%20was%20delisted%20from%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20in%20April%20after%20it%20fell%20to%209%20cents%20per%20share.%20Fisker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-sends-employees-possible-layoff-notice-2-months-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%3C%2Fa%3E%20staff%20in%20an%20April%20filing%20that%20they%20will%20be%20laid%20off%20if%20the%20company%20can't%20find%20a%20buyer%20or%20additional%20investor.%20The%20company%20brought%20in%20a%20chief%20restructuring%20officer%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewho%20was%20given%20%26quot%3Bsole%20authority%26quot%3B%20over%20some%20financial%20matters%2C%20including%20a%20potential%20sale%2C%20as%20part%20of%20an%20agreement%20with%20one%20of%20its%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELayoffs%20have%20stripped%20the%20staff%20to%20the%20bone.%20Its%20workforce%20is%20now%20less%20than%20100%20people%2C%20according%20to%20two%20sources%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20issue.%20Many%20of%20the%20workers%20who%20remain%20are%20involved%20in%20last-ditch%20efforts%20to%20offload%20Fisker's%20remaining%20inventory%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20does%20not%20have%20less%20than%20100%20workers%20left%20and%20continues%20to%20sell%20vehicles%20in%20the%20US%20and%20in%20Europe.%20It%20declined%20to%20specify%20how%20many%20workers%20remained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20workers%20have%20been%20dissatisfied%20with%20what%20they%20view%20as%20Henrik%20and%20Gupta-Fisker's%20inability%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-ceo-all-hands-meeting-announcing-layoffs-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etake%20accountability%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20their%20actions.%20A%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20pushed%20back%20on%20the%20comments%20questioning%20Henrik's%20business%20prowess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20a%20story%20of%20ego.%20He%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20car%20and%20stamp%20his%20name%20on%20it.%20Henrik%20is%20a%20great%20designer%2C%20but%20he%20doesn't%20have%20the%20business%20acumen%20beyond%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20individual%20who%20worked%20with%20Henrik%20at%20several%20companies%2C%20including%20his%20first%20automotive%20startup.%20%26quot%3BThe%20lessons%20he%20should%20have%20learned%20from%20the%20first%20startup%20were%20never%20implemented%20and%20he%20rushed%20a%20car%20to%20