g%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F12%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1718179260-5906.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fglobal-gender-gap-index-2024-indian-women-earn-rs-40-for-every-rs-100-indian-men-earn-124061200379_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20slipped%20two%20spots%20at%20129th%20rank%20in%20World%20Economic%20Forum's%20Global%20Gender%20Gap%20index%202024.%20While%20India's%20economic%20parity%20score%20has%20been%20improving%2C%20it's%206.2%20percentage%20points%20below%202012%20level%20of%2046%25%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fglobal-gender-gap-index-2024-indian-women-earn-rs-40-for-every-rs-100-indian-men-earn-124061200379_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fglobal-gender-gap-index-2024-indian-women-earn-rs-40-for-every-rs-100-indian-men-earn-124061200379_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fglobal-gender-gap-index-2024-indian-women-earn-rs-40-for-every-rs-100-indian-men-earn-124061200379_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Insurance%20Helped%2046%2C000%20Women%20Avoid%20Deadly%20Work%20In%20Scorching%20Heat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20Ahmedabad%2C%20temperatures%20climbed%20above%2043C%20(109F)%20every%20day%20between%20May%2019%20and%20May%2025%2C%20creating%20deadly%20hot%20working%20conditions%20for%20many%20of%20the%20labourers%20who%20keep%20the%20local%20economy%20humming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2040-year-old%20Lataben%20Arvindbhai%20Makwana%2C%20it%20was%20too%20unbearable%20to%20run%20her%20sewing%20machine%20inside%20her%20tin-roofed%20house%2C%20which%20has%20little%20ventilation%20and%20only%20a%20small%20ceiling%20fan.%20As%20a%20daily%20wage%20labourer%2C%20that%20meant%20she%20was%20not%20earning%20the%20money%20she%20needed%20to%20feed%20her%20kids%20and%20buy%20blood%20pressure%20medication%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20getting%20worse%20every%20summer%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Makwana%20said.%20The%20extreme%20heat%20is%20especially%20dangerous%20for%20people%20like%20her%20who%20suffer%20from%20hypertension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20climate%20change%20raising%20temperatures%20during%20heat%20waves%2C%20millions%20of%20Indians%20face%20a%20difficult%20choice%3A%20work%20in%20dangerous%20conditions%20or%20go%20hungry.%20But%20some%20women%20like%20Ms%20Makwana%20are%20now%20getting%20help%20from%20a%20program%20to%20make%20a%20third%20choice%3A%20stop%20working%20for%20at%20least%20a%20few%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20temperatures%20breached%2043.6C%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Ms%20Makwana%20and%20thousands%20of%20other%20women%20were%20told%20that%20ICICI%20Lombard%2C%20an%20insurance%20company%2C%20would%20pay%20them%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20daily%20wages.%20The%20program%20uses%20parametric%20insurance%2C%20which%20pays%20out%20when%20a%20particular%20metric%20is%20hit%2C%20such%20as%20a%20daily%20high%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2046%2C000%20women%20across%2022%20districts%20in%20India%20were%20paid%20%24340%2C000%20in%20total%20over%20last%20month's%20heat%20waves.%20About%2050%2C000%20women%20are%20enrolled%20in%20the%20program.%20Ms%20Makwana's%20insurance%20payout%20was%20Rs.%20750%20(%249)%2C%20enough%20to%20cover%20food%20and%20medication%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20(That%20sum%20came%20on%20top%20of%20a%20separate%20charity%20payout%20of%20Rs.%20400%20when%20the%20temperature%20breached%2040C%20the%20first%20time.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Self-Employed%20Women's%20Association%20labour%20union%20runs%20the%20insurance%20program.%20Its%20premium%20is%20paid%20for%20partly%20by%20the%20women%20enrolled%20in%20the%20program%2C%20with%20a%20charity%20covering%20the%20remaining%20portion.%20The%20pilot%20program%20launched%20last%20year%20and%20is%20set%20to%20run%20until%20April%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKathy%20Baughman%20McLeod%2C%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20Climate%20Resilience%20for%20All%2C%20the%20non-profit%20supporting%20the%20program%20through%20development%2C%20technical%20expertise%20and%20funding%2C%20says%20that%20it%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bsuccessful.%26quot%3B%20The%20charity%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20protecting%20women%20and%20vulnerable%20communities%20from%20extreme%20heat%2C%20plans%20to%20expand%20the%20insurance%20program%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaughman%20Mcleod%20hopes%20that%20the%20funders%20supporting%20the%20Indian%20program%20can%20continue%20to%20do%20so%20for%20a%20few%20more%20years.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20get%20SEWA's%202.9%20million%20members%20signed%20up%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20the%20plan%20to%20be%20funded%20entirely%20by%20women%20paying%20the%20premiums.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20experience%20is%20that%20poor%20women%20don't%20want%20charity%20always%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reema%20Nanavaty%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20SEWA.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20they%20see%20that%20this%20program%20is%20addressing%20their%20dire%20needs%2C%20I'm%20sure%20the%20women%20would%20start%20contributing%20toward%20the%20program.%26quot%3B%20The%20eventual%20plan%20would%20see%20the%20premium%20for%20each%20woman%20be%20about%20a%20day's%20wage%20every%20month%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETypical%20insurance%20programs%20work%20because%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20population%20that%20pays%20a%20premium%20asks%20for%20a%20payout%20in%20any%20given%20year.%20If%20most%20of%20them%20ask%20for%20a%20payout%20every%20year%2C%20which%20can%20be%20the%20case%20with%20heat%20waves%2C%20then%20next%20year's%20premiums%20have%20to%20rise%20to%20match%20the%20outgoings%20and%20that%20could%20easily%20become%20unaffordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaughman%20McLeod%20readily%20admits%20that%20she%20doesn't%20know%20if%20such%20an%20insurance%20program%20can%20become%20financially%20viable.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20solution%20for%20the%20urgent%20needs%20of%20right%20now%2C%20when%20women%20are%20developing%20blisters%2C%20or%20worse%2C%20suffering%20miscarriages%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20working%20in%20extreme%20heat%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20humanitarian%20crisis%20affecting%20those%20who%20are%20completely%20blameless%20for%20the%20climate%20impacts%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20insurance%20program%20cannot%20solve%20all%20the%20problems.%20So%20Climate%20Resilience%20for%20All%20and%20SEWA%20are%20working%20on%20a%20host%20of%20other%20interventions%2C%20including%20education%20programs%20that%20teach%20women%20how%20extreme%20heat%20affects%20health%20and%20what%20steps%20they%20can%20reasonably%20take%20to%20avoid%20suffering.%20SEWA's%20members%20work%20in%20more%20than%20100%20professions%2C%20from%20construction%20workers%20to%20outdoor%20food%20vendors.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20interventions%20vary%2C%20ranging%20from%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20carrying%20an%20umbrella%20for%20shade%20to%20working%20with%20a%20construction%20company%20to%20ensure%20access%20to%20cool%20drinking%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20cash%20in%20hand%20when%20it's%20needed%20can%20be%20crucial.%20Losing%20wages%20often%20forces%20the%20poorest%20women%20in%20India%20to%20go%20to%20informal%20money%20lenders%20that%20charge%20extortionary%20interest%20or%20personal%20favors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20value%20the%20insurance%20payment%20gives%20them%20is%20dignity%20and%20self-respect%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Nanavaty.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718181240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fungbf2pg_heatwave-generic_625x300_31_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-insurance-helped-46-000-w