-only-option%2Farticleshow%2F110934612.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20witnessed%20back-to-back%20three%20terror%20attacks%20in%20the%20span%20of%2072%20hours%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20National%20Conference%20(JNKC)%20president%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20that%20the%20military%20action%20will%20not%20solve%20anything%20and%20the%20only%20option%20is%20to%20hold%20talks%20with%20the%20neighbours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmilitary-action-will-not-solve-anything-after-3-terror-attacks-in-jk-farooq-abdullah-says-talk-with-neighbours-only-option%2Farticleshow%2F110934612.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20'Power%20Star'%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20Helped%20NDA%20Sweep%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor-politician%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20took%20oath%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20Chandrababu's%20Naidu%20cabinet%20today.%20Mr%20Naidu%20-%20who%20emerged%20as%20a%20kingmaker%20after%20the%20BJP%20fell%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20-%20has%20returned%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20for%20the%20fourth%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20known%20as%20'Power%20Star'%2C%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20the%20post%20of%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20it's%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJana%20Sena%20Chief%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20bringing%20the%20BJP%20and%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20together%20to%20take%20on%20the%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy-led%20YSR%20Congress%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tripartite%20alliance%20made%20a%20clean%20sweep%20by%20winning%20164%20Assembly%20seats.%20It%20also%20bagged%2021%20out%20of%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawan%20Kalyan%20had%20last%