gy%2Fgadgets%2Fxiaomi-14-civi-with-leica-camera-system-launched-in-india-price-offers-124061200424_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Fgadgets%2Fxiaomi-14-civi-with-leica-camera-system-launched-in-india-price-offers-124061200424_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Musk%20Had%20Sex%20With%20SpaceX%20Intern%2C%20Asked%20Woman%20To%20Have%20His%20Babies%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20having%20sexual%20relationships%20with%20two%20of%20his%20employees%2C%20including%20an%20intern%2C%20and%20asking%20another%20employee%20to%20have%20his%20babies%2C%20a%20report%20has%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20report%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20said%20the%20tech%20billionaire%20created%20a%20culture%20in%20his%20companies%20-%20both%20SpaceX%20and%20Tesla%20-%20which%20made%20the%20women%20employees%20uncomfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20allegations%20against%20Mr%20Musk%2C%20who%20has%20previously%20been%20accused%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cnof%20regularly%20using%20drugs%20like%20LSD%2C%20cocaine%2C%20ecstasy%2C%20mushrooms%20and%20ketamine%2C%20at%20times%20at%20work%20with%20board%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20SpaceX%20chief%20was%20accused%20of%20nurturing%20a%20%26quot%3Bhostile%20work%20environment%26quot%3B%20where%20jokes%20about%20sexual%20harassment%20were%20common%2C%20women%20were%20paid%20less%20than%20men%20and%20workers%20who%20complained%20were%20dismissed.%20In%20their%20complaints%2C%20former%20employees%20accused%20him%20of%20creating%20a%20sexist%20culture%20at%20the%20workplace%2C%20where%20sexual%20comments%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20harassment%20were%20tolerated%20or%20made%20light%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20report%20cited%20women%20employees%20at%20Tesla%20who%20claimed%20that%20they%20were%20shown%20%E2%80%9Can%20unusual%20amount%20of%20attention%20or%20pursued%E2%80%9D%20by%20Mr%20Musk.%20A%20SpaceX%20flight%20attendant%20had%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Musk%20exposed%20himself%20to%20her%20and%20offered%20to%20buy%20her%20a%20horse%20in%20exchange%20for%20sex%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20woman%2C%20who%20resigned%20from%20SpaceX%20in%202013%2C%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Musk%20had%20asked%20her%20to%20have%20his%20babies%2C%20on%20multiple%20occasions.%20The%20billionaire%2C%20who%20has%20at%20least%2010%20children%2C%20has%20said%20that%20the%20world%20faces%20an%20underpopulation%20crisis%20and%20people%20with%20high%20IQs%20should%20procreate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20claimed%20that%20a%20woman%20who%20worked%20at%20SpaceX%20received%20repeated%20invitations%20from%20Elon%20Musk%20to%20come%20to%20his%20house%20at%20night.%20The%20following%20details%20the%20text%20exchange%20between%20the%20two%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%3A%20%E2%80%9CCome%20by!Look%2C%20it's%20either%20me%20or%206am%20%5Bexercise%5D%20%3A)%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%3A%20%E2%80%9CJust%20finished%20the%20Model%203%20production%20call.%20It's%20def%20going%20to%20be%20hell%20for%20several%20more%20months.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%3A%20%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20coming%20over%3F%20If%20not%2C%20I%20will%20probably%20tranq%20out.%20Too%20stressed%20to%20sleep%20naturally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%3A%20%E2%80%9CProbably%20best%20if%20we%20don't%20see%20each%20other.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20the%20woman%20texted%20Mr%20Musk%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9COh%20man.%20I'm%20sorry%2C%20I'd%20already%20fallen%20asleep.%20I've%20been%20a%20late%20night%20person%20most%20of%20my%20life%20but%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20switch%20over%20because%20it%20seems%20responsible.%20Tbh.%20Sorry%20I%20crashed%20last%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20and%20Mr%20Musk's%20lawyers%20have%20rubbished%20the%20report%20claiming%20the%20information%20presented%20in%20it%20is%20full%20of%20%26quot%3Buntruths%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20untruths%2C%20mischaracterizations%2C%20and%20revisionist%20history%20in%20your%20email%20paint%20a%20completely%20misleading%20narrative.%20I%20continue%20to%20be%20amazed%20by%20what%20this%20extraordinary%20group%20of%20people%20are%20achieving%20every%20day%20even%20amidst%20all%20the%20forces%20acting%20against%20us.%20And%20Elon%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20humans%20I%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Gwynne%20Shotwell%2C%20SpaceX's%20president%20and%20chief%20operating%20officer%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718178900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fq4eqh9g8_elon-musk_625x300_24_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-had-sex-with-spacex-intern-asked-woman-to-have-his-babies-claims-report-5873064%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SpaceX%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20having%20sexual%20relationships%20with%20two%20of%20his%20employees%2C%20including%20an%20intern%2C%20and%20asking%20another%20employee%20to%20have%20his%20babies%2C%20a%20report%20has%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-had-sex-with-spacex-intern-asked-woman-to-have-his-babies-claims-report-5873064%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-had-sex-with-spacex-intern-asked-woman-to-have-his-babies-claims-report-5873064%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-had-sex-with-spacex-intern-asked-woman-to-have-his-babies-claims-report-5873064%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20Care%20If%20This%20Goes%20Viral%26quot%3B%3A%20Akram%20Exposes%20'Player-Rift'%20In%20Pak%20Team%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20has%20been%20und