%20(2003)%2C%20Namma%20Preethiya%20Ramu%20(2003)%2C%20Gaja%20(2008)%2C%20Saarathi%20(2011)%2C%20Krantiveera%20Sangolli%20Rayanna%20(2012)%2C%20Ambareesha%20(2014)%2C%20Tarak%20(2017)%2C%20Yajamana%20(2019)%20and%20Kurukshetra%20(2019).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20Darshan%C2%A0Thoogudeepa%20married%20his%20fiancee%20Vijayalakshmi%20in%202003.%20Together%2C%20the%20couple%20have%20a%20son%20named%20Vineesh.%20Mr%20Thoogudeepa%20also%20maintains%20a%20zoo%20near%20Malavalli%20and%20had%20earlier%20adopted%20a%20tiger%20cub.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4.%20Darshan%C2%A0Thoogudeepa%20shot%20to%20fame%20playing%20the%20righteous%20man%20on%20screen.%20However%2C%20the%20actor%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20controversies.%20In%202011%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20over%20a%20domestic%20violence%20complaint%20filed%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20spent%2014%20days%20in%20judicial%20custody.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20matter%20was%20resolved%20out%20of%20court%20and%20the%20actor%20publicly%20apologised%20to%20his%20fans%2C%20claiming%20he%20was%20intoxicated.%20Later%20in%202016%2C%20his%20wife%20again%20reported%20his%20'objectionable%20behaviour'%20to%20the%20police.%20Besides%20this%2C%20he%20also%20faced%20accusations%20of%20assaulting%20a%20waiter%20at%20a%20Mysuru%20hotel%20in%202021.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn5.%20In%20January%202024%2C%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20created%20a%20stir%20on%20social%20media%20after%20she%20shared%20a%20video%20on%20Instagram%20featuring%20several%20photographs%20of%20herself%20and%20Darshan.%20Sharing%20the%20video%20with%20the%20caption%2C%20%26quot%3B10%20years%20of%20our%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gowda%20hinted%20she%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20the%20married%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718177520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Feraumr3_darshan-thoogudeepa-srinivas-facebook_625x300_12_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarshan-thoogudeepa-arrested-in-murde