-economy-globally-world-bank-124061200394_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-remains-world-s-fastest-growing-major-economy-globally-world-bank-124061200394_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20Modi%203.0%20Should%20Be%20Committed%20To%20Bold%20Reforms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F3ng1iro_pm-modi-pti_625x300_01_May_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20has%20formed%20the%20government%20again%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20coalition%20at%20the%20union%20level%20in%20a%20decade.%20Unlike%20the%20coalition%20politics%20of%20pre-2014%2C%20infamous%20for%20policy%20paralysis%2C%20corruption%2C%20and%20inflation%2C%20this%20administration%20promises%20a%20different%20trajectory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%202014%2C%20coalition%20governments%20in%20India%20were%20synonymous%20with%20inefficiency%20and%20scandal.%20The%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20era%20(2004-2014)%20saw%20numerous%20high-profile%20scams%2C%20such%20as%20the%202G%20spectrum%20and%20coal%20allocation%20scandals%2C%20which%20eroded%20public%20trust%20and%20led%20to%20significant%20economic%20mismanagement.%20Policy%20paralysis%20was%20rampant%2C%20with%20crucial%20reforms%20stalling%20due%20to%20the%20constant%20need%20for%20political%20appeasement%20within%20the%20coalition%20framework.%20In%20contrast%2C%20since%202014%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20demonstrated%20decisive%20governance%2C%20focusing%20on%20economic%20reforms%20and%20transparency.%20Initiatives%20like%20Make%20in%20India%2C%20Digital%20India%2C%20and%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20have%20revitalised%20the%20economy%2C%20improved%20investor%20confidence%20and%20streamlined%20regulatory%20frameworks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leads%20this%20new%20coalition%20government%2C%20India%20must%20sustain%20its%20growth%20momentum%20through%20continued%20reforms.%20The%20government%20should%20be%20committed%20to%20bold%20reforms%20and%20process%20improvements%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20inefficiencies%20of%20past%20coalition%20politics%20are%20not%20repeated.%20A%20few%20areas%20where%20the%20new%20government%20should%20focus%20on%20are%20as%20follows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECapital%20Expenditure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20new%20government%20must%20prioritise%20capital%20expenditure%2C%20as%20it%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20more%20effective%20driver%20of%20economic%20growth%20than%20revenue%20expenditure.%20Previous%20budgets%20have%20highlighted%20the%20significant%20multiplier%20effect%20of%20capital%20expenditure%20(estimated%20at%202.45)%20compared%20to%20revenue%20expenditure%20(0.99).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestment%20in%20infrastructure%2C%20such%20as%20railways%2C%20national%20highways%2C%20ports%2C%20and%20waterways%2C%20should%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20strategy.%20These%20sectors%20not%20only%20stimulate%20economic%20activity%20but%20also%20ensure%20long-term%20developmental%20gains.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20projects%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20can%20implement%20directly%2C%20avoiding%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%20that%20often%20face%20delays%20due%20to%20coordination%20issues%20with%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clear%2C%20long-term%20fiscal%20management%20path%20is%20crucial.%20The%20government%20should%20articulate%20an%20explicit%20counter-cyclical%20fiscal%20policy%20that%20balances%20expansionary%20measures%20in%20downturns%20with%20contractionary%20measures%20in%20booms.%20This%20approach%20minimises%20distortions%20and%20promotes%20stability%20in%20tax%20rates.%20While%20expansionary%20policies%20are%20more%20politically%20palatable%2C%20contractionary%20measures%20are%20equally%20essential%20to%20manage%20economic%20cycles%20effectively.%20The%20emphasis%20should%20be%20on%20capital%20expenditure%20to%20navigate%20economic%20fluctuations%2C%20given%20that%20revenue%20expenditure%20tends%20to%20be%20inflexible.%20Ensuring%20transparency%20and%20consistency%20in%20these%20policies%20will%20build%20confidence%20and%20predictability%20in%20the%20fiscal%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EManaging%20Demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20recent%20analysis%20by%20EAC-PM%20members%20Sajjid%20Chinoy%20and%20Neelkanth%20Mishra%20has%20flagged%20that%20demand%2C%20especially%20rural%20demand%2C%20is%20a%20concern.%20Public%20investment%20alone%20cannot%20sustain%20economic%20growth%20indefinitely%3B%20the%20private%20sector%20must%20step%20up.%20While%20real%20estate%20investment%20has%20surged%2C%20corporate%20capital%20expenditure%20lags%20due%20to%20insufficient%20demand%20visibility.%20This%20is%20evident%20in%20stagnant%20capacity%20utilisation%20rates%2C%20single-digit%20nominal%20sales%20growth%2C%20and%20weak%20core%20inflation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountercyclical%20fiscal%20and%20monetary%20policies%20are%20constrained%2C%20making%20it%20crucial%20for%20the%20union%20government%20to%20boost%20demand%20through%20private%20consumption%20and%20exports.%20Consumption%2C%20growing%20at%20just%204.2%25%20over%20five%20years%2C%20has%20been%20hampered%20by%20a%20dichotomous%20labour%20market%20and%20declining%20real%20per-capita%20consumption.%20A%20consumption%20revival%2C%20alongside%20broadening%20export%20contributions%2C%20is%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployment%20growth%2C%20lagging%20behind%20demographic%20changes%2C%20needs%20focus%2C%20with%20many%20recent%20jobs%20in%20agriculture%20and%20a%20shift%20toward%20capital-intensive%20manufacturing.%20To%20make%20labour%20more%20attractive%2C%20comprehensive%20policies%20are%20required%2C%20from%20improving%20education%2C%20health%2C%20and%20skills%20to%20supporting%20labour-intensive%20industries.%20This%20should%20be%20complemented%20with%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20four%20new%20labour%20codes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20need%20to%20shift%20the%20focus%20from%20deficit%20indicators%20to%20debt%20indicators%20as%20they%20provide%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20measure%20of%20fiscal%20health.%20The%20debt-to-GDP%20ratio%20offers%20a%20clearer%20picture%20of%20fiscal%20sustainability%2C%20reflecting%20the%20cumulative%20impact%20of%20fiscal%20policies.%20This%20approach%20accounts%20for%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20difference%20between%20interest%20rates%20and%20growth%20rates%20and%20the%20primary%20budget%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrioritising%20debt%20management%20over%20deficit%20targets%20will%20help%20create%20a%20stable%20fiscal%20environment%2C%20reducing%20volatility%20caused%20by%20fluctuating%20GDP%20estimates.%20A%20well-defined%20debt%20management%20strategy%20will%20enhance%20fiscal%20resilience%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETax%20Reforms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20direct%20and%20indirect%20tax%20reforms%20are%20pivotal%20for%20increasing%20revenue.%20The%20government%20should%20focus%20on%20broadening%20the%20tax%20base%2C%20reducing%20exemptions%2C%20and%20improving%20compliance%20to%20enhance%20tax%20buoyancy.%20Direct%20tax%20reforms%2C%20including%20a%20comprehensive%20overhaul%20of%20corporate%20income%20tax%20(CIT)%20and%20personal%20income%20tax%20(PIT)%2C%20are%20long%20overdue.%20Simplifying%20the%20tax%20structure%20and%20eliminating%20exemptions%20will%20reduce%20compliance%20costs%20and%20litigation.%20For%20GST%2C%20expanding%20the%20tax%20base%20to%20include%20more%20goods%20and%20services%20and%20rationalising%20tax%20rates%20will%20improve%20efficiency%20and%20revenue%20collection.%20The%20GST%20Council%20should%20convene%20regularly%20to%20address%20these%20reforms%20and%20ensure%20the%20system%20evolves%20to%20meet%20economic%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20expenditure%20reform%20is%20essential%20to%20manage%20fiscal%20pressures.%20While%20some%20expenditures%2C%20such%20as%20interest%20payments%2C%20mandated%20transfers%2C%20wages%2C%20and%20pensions%2C%20are%20relatively%20fixed%2C%20there%20is%20significant%20scope%20to%20rationalise%20subsidies%20and%20various%20schemes.%20The%20government%20should%20prioritise%20and%20streamline%20public%20expenditure%2C%20rationalise%20major%20schemes%20and%20focus%20on%20central%20sector%20initiatives.%20Reforming%20food%2C%20fertilizer%2C%20and%20petroleum%20subsidies%20and%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%20will%20align%20fiscal%20policies%20with%20economic%20realities%2C%20ensuring%20efficient%20and%20transparent%20resource%20allocation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20focusing%20on%20these%20areas%2C%20the%20new%20NDA%20government%20can%20achieve%20sustainable%20economic%20growth%20and%20fiscal%20stability%2C%20ensuring%20that%20India%20continues%20to%20progress%20towards%20its%20economic%20milestones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bibek%20Debroy%20is%20Chairman%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20Aditya%20Sinha%20is%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%2C%20Research%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister)%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718177340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F3ng1iro_pm-modi-pti_625x300_01_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-modi-3-0-should-be-committed-to-bold-reforms-5872568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20government%20should%20be%20