p%3EGradually%2C%20Payden's%20talents%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20Scudder%2C%20Stevens%20%26amp%3B%20Clark%2C%20an%20investment%20counselling%20firm%2C%20where%20she%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20partner%20%E2%80%93%20a%20milestone%20that%20set%20her%20on%20a%20path%20to%20founding%20her%20own%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201983%2C%20at%2052%2C%20Ms%20Payden%20co-founded%20Payden%20%26amp%3B%20Rygel%20with%20colleague%20Sandra%20Rygel%2C%20which%20focused%20on%20fixed%20income%20and%20global%20markets.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20always%20worries.%20When%20I%20set%20up%20the%20company%2C%20I%20worried%20I%20wouldn't%20get%20clients.%20But%20that%20was%20no%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20in%20over%20four%20decades%2C%20the%20firm%20has%20grown%20into%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20private%20money%20managers%2C%20with%20%24162%20billion%20in%20assets%20under%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20success%2C%20Payden%20remains%20humble%20and%20dedicated%20to%20philanthropy.%20She%20has%20donated%20millions%20to%20causes%20ranging%20from%20animal%20welfare%20to%20education%2C%20leaving%20a%20lasting%20impact%20on%20institutions%20like%20Trinity%20College%20and%20universities%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718177100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fvduvd8ug_joan-payden_625x300_12_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fat-92-joan-payden-is-among-americas-richest-self-made-women-her-net-worth-is-5872208%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ninety-two-year-old%20Joan%20Payden%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20net%20worth%20of%20%24700%20million%2C%20is%20among%20America's%20richest%20self-made%20women%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%20Born%20in%20Derby%2C%20Connecticut%20in%201931%2C%20Payden%20spent%20her%20teenage%20years%20in%20Indonesia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engageme