vironmental%20issues%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20recall.%20However%2C%20when%20it%20came%20to%20taking%20action%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20often%20stumbled%20upon%20articles%20highlighting%20the%20escalating%20plastic%20waste%20crisis%20in%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CI%20became%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20and%20as%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20I%20felt%20compelled%20to%20seek%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nikhil%20acknowledges%20that%20there%20are%20a%20few%20alternative%20options%20to%20plastic%2C%20he%20was%20determined%20to%20develop%20a%20product%20that%20resembled%20plastic%20in%20appearance%20and%20affordability%20but%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F279849%2Fsustainable-pune-startup-studio-alternatives-upcycles-old-shipping-container-houses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmentally%20friendly.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bottles%20can%20decompose%20in%20180%20days.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-i