ng%20from%20electricity%20to%20internet%20connectivity%2C%20he%20pursued%20his%20passion%20in%20the%20era%20of%202g%20cellular%20network.%20Watching%20movies%20like%20The%20Matrix%2C%20Live%20Free%20or%20Die%20Hard%2C%20opened%20his%20eyes%20to%20the%20world%20of%20ethical%20hacking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%20bought%20their%20first%20computer%20in%202012%2C%20post%20which%2C%20the%20young%20boy%20would%20spend%20hours%20on%20the%20internet%20learning%20the%20basics%20of%20hardware%2C%20networking%20and%20programming.%20He%20learnt%20from%20tutorials%20on%20Google%20and%20YouTube%2C%20following%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20late%20Kevin%20Mitnick%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20hackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20that%20we%20can%20secure%20data%20for%20organisations.%20Even%20though%20companies%20have%20their%20own%20security%20teams%2C%20they%20invite%20ethical%20hackers%20to%20report%20vulnerabilities%20in%20their%20data%20through%20their%20responsible%20disclosure%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20343%20million%20people%20have%20been%20the%20victims%20of%20cyber%20attacks%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Forbes%20report.%20Data%20breaches%20also%20saw%20a%2072%20percent%20increase%20in%202023%20compared%20to%202021%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20need%20for%20ethical%20hackers%20and%20cyber%20security%20experts%20all%20the%20more%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Class%2012%2C%20Muneeb%20pursued%20a%20B.Tech%20in%20Computer%20Science%20in%20a%20college%20which%20was%2080%20km%20away.%20The%20daily%20travel%20and%20classes%20left%20him%20with%20no%20time%20to%20pursue%20his%20passion.%20Supported%20by%20his%20father%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20drop%20out%20in%20the%20second%20year%20to%20focus%20entirely%20on%20ethical%20hacking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20either%20complete%20my%20engineering%20degree%20or%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C