ole%20in%20fortifying%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20nature.%20She%20says%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20Mahima%E2%80%99s%20passion%20rubbed%20off%20on%20her%2C%20her%20husband%2C%20and%20their%20daughter%20Ashima%2C%20and%20they%20grew%20as%20intrigued%20by%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinati%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20based%20in%20London%2C%20sees%20those%20years%20of%20innocence%20as%20the%20fabric%20that%20wove%20together%20the%20story%20of%20O%E2%80%99Land%20Plantation%20Stays%20%E2%80%94%20a%20120-acre%20estate%20which%20she%20manages.%20Set%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20of%20the%20Nilgiris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20geographic%20salient%20that%20is%20spread%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%2C%20the%20stay%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20responsible%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20ever%20happen%20to%20be%20in%20Coonoor%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20recommend%3A%20Get%20into%20the%20car%2C%20stock%20it%20up%20with%20provisions%20that%20will%20last%20you%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20then%20drive.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20the%20unsealed%20roads%20daunt%20you.%20Look%20for%20company%20in%20the%20spectacular%20scenery%20instead.%20Keep%20driving%20until%20you%20spot%20a%20carpet%20of%20green.%20This%20will%20be%20your%20first%20indication%20of%20having%20arrived%20at%20the%20O%E2%80%99Land%20Plantation%20Stay.%20The%20place%20is%20a%20great%20draw%20for%20bids%2C%20who%20are%20attracted%20by%20the%20glorious%20view%20%E2%80%94%20a%20set%20of%20three%20cottages%20hugged%20by%20a%20verdant%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20Vinati%20and%20Pavan%2C%20the%20brains%20behind%20this%20oasis%20emphasise%2C%20it%20makes%20for%20a%20great%20relaxing%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-